                                    </div>
                                    <div class="desc" style="color:white; font-size:10px;">Baps Confirm - Posting</div>
                                    <div class="desc" style="color:black; font-size:large;"><b>1 D</b></div>
                                </div>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">
                            <a class="dashboard-stat dashboard-stat-v2 green" id="divSubmitDocInvoice">
                                <div class="visual">
                                    <i class="fa fa-bar-chart-o"></i>
